loops-continue_key1: Aap pehle iss video ko dekhein `continue` command ka `loop` mei kaam samajhne ke liye. Iss understanding ko use kar kar, humein aage likhe hue `code` ka dry run karna hai.
loops-continue_key2: Agar aap yeh diagram dekhoge toh aap samjhoge, ki `continue` command se hum `loop` mei
loops-continue_key3: jo bhi `continue` ke baad `code` hai uss `loop` mei, woh `execute` nahi hota
loops-continue_key4: `loop` ki starting mei `control flow` pahuch jaata hai
loops-continue_key5: Ab iss idea ko use karte hue in example `codes` ka `dry run` karein.
loops-continue_key6: __Ek baar dhyaan se dekhein ki break aur continue mei kya difference hai__
loops-continue_key7: Iss program ko `execute` karo. Iss program ko bina `continue` `statement` ke dobara likho.
